Package: EuPathDB
Title: Provides access to pathogen annotation resources available on EuPathDB databases
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Keith", "Hughitt", email = "keith.hughitt@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Keith Hughitt <keith.hughitt@gmail.com>
Description: Brings together annotation resources from the various EuPathDB
    databases (PlasmoDB, ToxoDB, TriTrypDB, etc.) and makes them
    available in R using the AnnotationHub framework.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5),
    Biobase,
    GenomicRanges,
    AnnotationHub (>= 2.13.7),
Imports: AnnotationHubData, Biostrings, BiocManager, utils
Suggests:
    dplyr,
    knitr,
    BiocStyle,
    rmarkdown,
    jsonlite
biocViews: DataImport
License: Artistic-2.0
URL: https://github.com/khughitt/EuPathDB
BugReports: https://github.com/khughitt/EuPathDB/issues
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
